**What is Combine ?**
- Provides a declarative Swift API.

*Publisher:* 
Publisher is a protocol which has two associated types(Output, Failure)
Publisher has one key function which is called subscribe.
Combine provides a number of additional convenience publishers:
- Just, Future, Deferred, Empty, Sequence, Fail, Record, Share, Multicast, ObservableObject, @Published.
Note: There are some Apple API outside of Combine provide publishers as well 

